In environment H0 : forall x y : nat, x ≲ y -> x <= y x, y : nat H : ⟬ x ⟭ ⪯ ⟬ y ⟭ H1 : forall x y : nat, (x ?= y) <> Lt -> y <= x Unable to unify "?M1856 <= ?M1855" with "x ≲ y".

original: split. - apply binary_le_lb_mask. - intros H. apply binary_le_le. apply Nat.compare_ge_iff. intros contra. assert (contra2 : ⟬ y ⟭ ⪯ ⟬ x ⟭) by (rewrite lb_mask_equiv_rst_Symmetric in H; auto). apply (lb_mask_equiv_rst_Transitive _ _ _ H contra2) in binary_le_refl. destruct (Nat.lt_trichotomy x y) as [|[|]]. + contradiction binary_le_refl. + rewrite e in H. contradiction Nat.lt_irrefl with x. + contradiction contra.
